      "writtenOn": "2026-06-10T13:21:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Agreed — #943 is stale (predates allows/isValid), too broad (covers must/range/etc.), and carries unrelated discussion. A small dedicated proposal for these predicate builtins, matching the spec in this stack, makes sense, and we\u0027d then close #943 in favor of it plus separate issues for the others (must already has #575).\n\nThat needs a new issue to be filed; I\u0027ve left the #943 link in place for now and will swap it for the new proposal once it exists. Leaving open to track that.",
